&lt;p&gt;HULK. We made a world. I was the Green King. And Caiera the Oldstrong was my
queen. But your &amp;ldquo;heroes&amp;rdquo; sent a bomb. Killed a million people. Now this
city will fall. You have twenty-four hours to evacuate. &lt;br/&gt; &lt;span class="citation-ref"&gt;&lt;a href="#WorldWarHulk-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>